[Amit Varma]: Do you want to read more? I've put in a lot of work in recent years in building

00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:34.600
[Amit Varma]: a reading habit. This means that I read more books, but I also read more long-form

00:03:34.600 --> 00:03:38.120
[Amit Varma]: articles and essays. There's a world of knowledge available through the internet,

00:03:38.120 --> 00:03:42.600
[Amit Varma]: but the problem we all face is, how do we navigate this knowledge? How do we know

00:03:42.600 --> 00:03:46.880
[Amit Varma]: what to read? How do we put the right incentives in place? Well, I discovered

