01:46:11.360 --> 01:46:15.320
[Guest]: person that child's life when we wrote that story a lot of people were taken

01:46:15.320 --> 01:46:18.360
[Guest]: aback my colleague Sowmya Rajendran wrote it I don't remember if she was she

01:46:18.360 --> 01:46:21.200
[Guest]: was not a newsman she was a freelancer so I contacted her and told her can you

01:46:21.200 --> 01:46:25.240
[Guest]: write in this angle and she agreed with me and it became very viral a lot of

01:46:25.240 --> 01:46:30.520
[Guest]: people shared it and I realized that we are not telling stories from a woman's

01:46:30.520 --> 01:46:35.280
[Guest]: perspective why why should every story be about questioning Manju Aryan why

