01:46:39.360 --> 01:46:45.320
[Guest]: right so from then on for me in the news minute journey from that story I decided

01:46:45.320 --> 01:46:48.640
[Guest]: that if I want to look at a story I am NOT going to think like Danya in times

01:46:48.640 --> 01:46:53.600
[Guest]: now I'm going to think differently I mean I've had many learning lessons when

01:46:53.600 --> 01:46:58.360
[Guest]: in times now itself there was a story I covered of a rape of a child by her own

01:46:58.360 --> 01:47:03.320
[Guest]: father he was what he wasn't he was working with the embassy here he was a

01:47:03.320 --> 01:47:07.560
[Guest]: foreign national was a French citizen and we covered the news a lot so in my

01:47:07.560 --> 01:47:11.040
[Guest]: mind I'm thinking justice for the child justice for the child right and in my

01:47:11.040 --> 01:47:16.200
[Guest]: pursuit for justice I am putting out all sorts of gory stories how she was

01:47:16.200 --> 01:47:21.800
[Guest]: violated what was the exact nature of rape etc because I am thinking justice

01:47:21.800 --> 01:47:25.720
[Guest]: justice justice then the mother sat me down and said I understand your

01:47:25.720 --> 01:47:29.620
