02:07:15.440 --> 02:07:19.400
[Amit Varma]: I've all my life thought of myself as a writer and right now I'm not writing we

02:07:19.400 --> 02:07:22.520
[Amit Varma]: are talking right and I will at some point do things on YouTube as well and

