[Guest]: Dhanya and I resigned but I had three months notice period so eventually I

02:14:33.240 --> 02:14:38.920
[Guest]: worked till March 31st I mean it was it was a decision which is coming I got

02:14:38.920 --> 02:14:44.120
[Guest]: tired of TV and I felt TV was not changing it from it was exciting in the

