[Guest]: beginning you know to stand on live from 6 o'clock in the morning to 9 o'clock in

02:14:47.720 --> 02:14:52.480
[Guest]: the night every time breaking news happens I'm I have abundance of energy I

02:14:52.480 --> 02:14:58.040
[Guest]: have no problem with that but I felt we were too agenda driven so much agenda in

02:14:58.040 --> 02:15:06.000
