02:15:26.720 --> 02:15:30.600
[Guest]: slowly I started thinking there is an undercurrent of an agenda and of course

02:15:30.600 --> 02:15:33.920
[Guest]: is pushing the South narrative plus the toxicity in the news it was all

02:15:33.920 --> 02:15:39.320
